Class MainActivity.SearchDialogFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.app.Dialog
      • triageapp.activities.MainActivity.SearchDialogFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DialogInterface, KeyEvent.Callback, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, Window.Callback
    Enclosing class:
    MainActivity

    public class MainActivity.SearchDialogFragment
extends Dialog
    A internal Dialog box class for looking up a Patient. Prompts a user to look up a Patient by entering the health card number. Displayed for two functions: to look up a Patient's info, or to view a Patient's medical record.
